node.text: Therapy can be daunting, especially if you don’t know where to start. In honor of Bebe Moore Campbell Minoirty Mental Health Awareness Month, real therapists @hellodrjoy and @beverleyandre_ break down how to find a therapist that’s right for you — and what to do if your therapist isn’t a match.
